THERE have been questions around the wearing of masks in
the fight against Coronavirus. Answering the question, Mzansi Health Minister Dr Zweli
Mkhize said that there is no question about it. “Masks can assist in containing
the spread of the virus, especially for those who are coughing, sneezing or are
infected,” said Mkhize. Mkhize further shared information on how to put
on, use, take off and dispose of a mask. 